class base_rnn(torch.nn.Module):
    """ basic RNN """
    def __init__(self):
        super().__init__()
        #self.cnn = torch.nn.LazyConv1d(10,kernel_size=1)
        self.rnn = torch.nn.RNN(input_size=49,hidden_size=10,
                               batch_first=True)
        self.linear = torch.nn.LazyLinear(1)
        
        
    def forward(self,x):
        #print(x.shape)
        #x = self.cnn(x)
        #print(x.shape)
#        x = x.permute(0,2,1)
        #print(x.shape)
        batch_first, hidden  = self.rnn(x)
        x = batch_first[:,:,-1]
        x = self.linear(x)
        return x
